          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1696239823317-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>Italian hard cheese </strong>finely</p><p>Combine your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix</strong> and <strong>mayo</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>cider</strong> <strong>vinegar</strong>, <strong>Dijon</strong> <strong>mustard</strong>, <strong>half </strong>the <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>creamy slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1696239827380-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1696239827380-x400.jpg",
